library(e1071)
Auto.copy = Auto[,c(-1,-9)]
Auto.copy$mpgbin = as.factor(mpg.bin)
range = list(cost=c(0.001,0.01,1,10,100,1000,10000))
tune.linear = tune(svm,mpgbin~.,data=Auto.copy,kernel="linear",ranges=range)
